Title: Doja Cat - Ain't Shit (Official Live Performance) | Vevo
Description:
Doja Cat - Ain't Shit (Official Live Performance)  |  Vevo

Spend time roaming ‚ÄòPlanet Her‚Äô and you‚Äôll know that Doja Cat‚Äôs artistic vision never sleeps. The singer‚Äôs desire to develop rich musical and visual environments for her fans is job one, and this new album, her third after ‚ÄòAmala‚Äô and ‚ÄòHot Pink,‚Äô is her most fully-realized statement yet. Doja has told interviewers that she wanted to take chances, try new approaches, and create ‚Äúotherworldly‚Äù sounds. Job done. The same goes for these new Official Live Performances. After meeting with the singer and her creative team, our production crew got to work in a canyon outside of LA. There, assuring that ‚Äúotherworldly‚Äù request was appropriately fleshed out, we built a 48‚Äô stage in the center of a rocky crag. Doja, banking on a combo of skills, artistry, and perseverance, did the rest. ‚ÄúAin‚Äôt Shit‚Äù finds her chastising those who don‚Äôt live up to her standards, indictments leveled with some dreamy grooves behind them. Watch her prowl the stage. She‚Äôs as comfy in a Cali desert as she was in that giant saucer of milk she glided through in our ‚ÄúStreets‚Äù LIFT performance last year. Emotional candor and artistic command is everywhere in ‚ÄúAin‚Äôt Shit.‚Äù Stay close to the Vevo social accounts. There‚Äôs more on the way.
